<br>
Sounds to me from their rules they tried to make it self regulating in a few ways. First if a guild were to go up there without knowledge of the system they would quickly learn that there are &quot;several&quot; guilds participating, therefore, they would find themeselves at odds with several guilds not just one voice if they didn't heed to the system. That could have several impacts. <br>
